name: lds-heart

style: .loader{-webkit-animation:rotate 2s linear infinite normal;animation:rotate 2s linear infinite normal;height:1rem;position:relative;width:1rem;margin:0 auto;margin-top:25px}.loader__ball{animation:move1 1s ease-in-out infinite alternate;background-color:#fff;border-radius:50%;height:100%;position:absolute;width:100%}.loader__ball:nth-of-type(2){animation-name:move2}.loader__ball:nth-of-type(3){animation-name:move3}@keyframes rotate{from{transform:rotate(0)}to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}@keyframes move1{0%,5%{transform:translate(0,0)}to{transform:translate(0,-100%)}}@keyframes move2{0%,5%{transform:translate(0,0)}to{transform:translate(100%,100%)}}@keyframes move3{0%,15%{transform:translate(0)}to{transform:translate(-100%,100%)}}

style: .pacman{position:relative;margin-top:25px}.pacman div:nth-child(1),.pacman div:nth-child(2){width:50px;height:25px;position:absolute;top:calc(50% - 25px);left:calc(50% - 50px / 2 - 50px)}.pacman div:nth-child(2){transform:rotateX(.5turn) translateY(-25px)}.pacman div:nth-child(1):after,.pacman div:nth-child(2):after{content:'';display:block;width:50px;height:25px;background:#fff;border-radius:25px 25px 0 0;transform-origin:50% 100%;animation:pacman .5s linear infinite}@keyframes pacman{25%{transform:rotate(-45deg)}50%{transform:rotate(0)}}.pacman div:nth-child(3),.pacman div:nth-child(4),.pacman div:nth-child(5){width:10px;height:10px;background:#fff;border-radius:50%;position:absolute;top:calc(50% - 10px / 2);left:calc(50% - 10px / 2 + 45px);animation:beans 1s linear infinite}.pacman div:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.33s}.pacman div:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.66s}@keyframes beans{to{transform:translate(-110px);opacity:.7}}
